  <entry>
    <title>git报错errno 10054</title>
    <link href="https://mainkeys.github.io/2021/09/10/git%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%E8%B8%A9%E5%9D%91/"/>
    <id>https://mainkeys.github.io/2021/09/10/git%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%E8%B8%A9%E5%9D%91/</id>
    <published>2021-09-10T04:33:21.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-09-10T06:06:10.474Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>昨天还可以git push代码到远程仓库，今天使用hexo d上传git仓库是时报了这个错：fatal: unable to access ‘<a href="https://github.com/.......&#39;">https://github.com/.......&#39;</a>: OpenSSL SSL_read: Connection was reset, errno 10054<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/0913af988d1c42539d611a0681cba738.png?process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAajogKQ==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16"></p><p>产生原因：一般是这是因为服务器的SSL证书没有经过第三方机构的签署，所以才报错</p><p>参考网上解决办法：解除ssl验证后，再上传就OK了<br><code>git config --global http.sslVerify &quot;false&quot;</code><br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/f389967d3ce94127b09feb5ee55a3e1c.png?process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAajogKQ==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;昨天还可以git push代码到远程仓库，今天使用hexo d上传git仓库是时报了这个错：fatal: unable to access ‘&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/.......&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;https://github.com/.....</summary>
      
    
    
    
